{"abstract":[{"text":"It’s easy to write an app for iOS, however writing a great app takes effort. iOS Engineers will show you how to improve your app’s responsiveness and performance, while polishing the overall user experience. Discover new techniques for saving your app’s state, starting quickly on cold launch, improving user awareness by utilizing animations, and working efficiently with network resources and GCD.","type":"text"}],"kind":"article","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-105-polishing-your-app-tips-and-tricks-to-improve-responsiveness-and-performance"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"role":"sampleCode","roleHeading":"WWDC11","title":"Polishing your App: Tips and Tricks to Improve Responsiveness and Performance"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-105-Polishing-your-App-Tips-and-Tricks-to-Improve-Responsiveness-and-Performance"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/105\/","overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"references":{"WWDC11.jpeg":{"identifier":"WWDC11.jpeg","alt":nu